BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 168.96 610 Td (WHAT IS ANGER?) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 600 m 382 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 575 Td (Anger is a natural human emotion that signals something feels wrong.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 559 Td (It becomes a problem when it is too intense, too frequent, or leads) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 543 Td (to harmful actions. Anger is not just 'losing your temper' - it is a) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 527 Td (complex emotional response involving thoughts, physical sensations,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 511 Td (and behaviors.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 495 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 479 Td (PRIMARY vs SECONDARY EMOTION:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 463 Td (Anger often masks deeper feelings like hurt, fear, or shame.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 447 Td (Learning to identify what is underneath your anger is the first step.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 431 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 415 Td (THE COST OF UNMANAGED ANGER:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 399 Td (- Damaged relationships with partner, children, friends) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 383 Td (- Health problems: high blood pressure, heart disease, headaches) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 367 Td (- Career consequences: lost jobs, missed promotions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 351 Td (- Legal issues: assault charges, restraining orders) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 335 Td (- Emotional toll: guilt, shame, isolation) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 319 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 303 Td (THE GOOD NEWS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 287 Td (Anger CAN be managed. This workbook will teach you practical tools) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 271 Td (to understand your triggers, interrupt the anger cycle, and respond) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 255 Td (rather than react. Change is possible at any age.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
