BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 132.0 610 Td (THE ANGER CYCLE EXPLAINED) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 600 m 382 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 575 Td (Anger follows a predictable cycle. Understanding this cycle gives) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 560 Td (you power to interrupt it at multiple points.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 545 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 530 Td (PHASE 1: TRIGGER \(The Spark\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 515 Td (Something happens externally or internally that starts the process.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 500 Td (This can be an event, memory, thought, or physical sensation.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 485 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 470 Td (PHASE 2: ESCALATION \(The Build-Up\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 455 Td (Physical arousal increases. Thoughts become more negative and rigid.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 440 Td (This is where early warning signs appear. You still have choices here.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 425 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 410 Td (PHASE 3: CRISIS \(The Explosion\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (Anger reaches peak intensity. Rational thinking shuts down.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 380 Td (Fight-or-flight takes over. Harmful actions are most likely here.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 365 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 350 Td (PHASE 4: RECOVERY \(The Cool-Down\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 335 Td (Physiological arousal gradually decreases. This takes 20-60 minutes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 320 Td (Do NOT try to resolve issues during this phase.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 305 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 290 Td (PHASE 5: AFTERMATH \(The Consequences\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 275 Td (Guilt, shame, damage assessment. Opportunity for repair and learning.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 260 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 245 Td (KEY INSIGHT: The best intervention point is Phase 2 \(Escalation\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 230 Td (Once you hit Phase 3, your rational brain is offline.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 215 Td (Learn to recognize Phase 2 and use your Time-Out technique.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
