BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 142.07999999999998 610 Td (THE TIME-OUT TECHNIQUE) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 600 m 382 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 575 Td (The Time-Out is your EMERGENCY BRAKE. Use it when you feel yourself) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 560 Td (entering Phase 2 of the anger cycle.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 545 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 530 Td (STEP 1: RECOGNIZE) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 515 Td (Notice your early warning signs \(refer to your checklist on page 3\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 500 Td (Say to yourself: 'I am getting angry. I need a time-out.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 485 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 470 Td (STEP 2: ANNOUNCE) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 455 Td (Tell the other person calmly: 'I need to take a break. I will be) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 440 Td (back in [specific time].' Do NOT just storm out.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 425 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 410 Td (STEP 3: LEAVE) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (Go to a pre-planned location. Do NOT drive. Do NOT drink alcohol.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 380 Td (Go for a walk, sit in another room, or step outside.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 365 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 350 Td (STEP 4: COOL DOWN \(minimum 20 minutes\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 335 Td (Use deep breathing: inhale 4 counts, hold 4, exhale 6.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 320 Td (Do NOT rehearse the argument in your head.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 305 Td (Use physical activity: push-ups, walk, squeeze stress ball.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 290 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 275 Td (STEP 5: RETURN) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 260 Td (Come back at the time you said. If still escalated, ask for more) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 245 Td (time. Address the issue when BOTH people are calm.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 230 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 215 Td (MY TIME-OUT PLAN:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 200 Td (I will go to: _________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 185 Td (I will do: ___________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 170 Td (My cool-down time: ___________ minutes) Tj ET

endstream
