BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 455 Td (PASSIVE: Never mention it, resent them forever) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 440 Td (ASSERTIVE: 'I lent you $X on [date]. I need that back by [date].) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 425 Td (  Can we agree on a plan?') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 410 Td () Tj ET
