BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 132.0 610 Td (CONFLICT RESOLUTION STEPS) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 600 m 382 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 575 Td (Follow these steps AFTER both parties are calm \(not during anger\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 561 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 547 Td (STEP 1: Choose the right time and place) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 533 Td (  - Both people must be calm \(at least 20 min after conflict\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 519 Td (  - Private location, no audience, no distractions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 505 Td (  - Ask: 'Is now a good time to talk about what happened?') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 477 Td (STEP 2: Define the problem WITHOUT blame) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 463 Td (  - Use I-statements, not You-statements) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 449 Td (  - Stick to ONE issue at a time \(no 'kitchen sinking'\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 435 Td (  - State facts, not interpretations) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 421 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 407 Td (STEP 3: Listen actively) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 393 Td (  - Let them finish without interrupting) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td (  - Reflect back what you heard: 'So you felt...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 365 Td (  - Ask: 'Did I understand you correctly?') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 351 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 337 Td (STEP 4: Acknowledge their perspective) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 323 Td (  - Validation is NOT agreement. Say: 'I can see why you felt...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 309 Td (  - Find the grain of truth in their complaint) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 295 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 281 Td (STEP 5: Brainstorm solutions together) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 267 Td (  - What would work for BOTH of us?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 253 Td (  - Be willing to compromise \(not capitulate\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 239 Td (  - Agree on specific actions going forward) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 225 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 211 Td (STEP 6: Follow through and check back) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 197 Td (  - Do what you agreed to do) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 183 Td (  - Check in: 'How is this working for you?') Tj ET

endstream
endobj
